1
00:01:10,160 --> 00:01:10,720
[Recently,]

2
00:01:10,840 --> 00:01:11,760
[the wealthy family scam was exposed.]

3
00:01:12,120 --> 00:01:13,120
[Xu Meng impersonated Lan Hewei,]

4
00:01:13,400 --> 00:01:15,240
[playing out a real-life version of the heiress.]

5
00:01:16,080 --> 00:01:18,280
[As the true chairman of the Blue Crane Group,]

6
00:01:18,680 --> 00:01:19,560
[I hereby announce]

7
00:01:20,520 --> 00:01:21,600
[that the resort project]

8
00:01:21,960 --> 00:01:23,560
[of the Blue Crane Group will be officially handed over]

9
00:01:23,560 --> 00:01:24,960
[to the Lin Group.]

10
00:01:25,440 --> 00:01:26,520
How could this be?

11
00:01:46,960 --> 00:01:47,560
Honey,

12
00:01:48,240 --> 00:01:49,320
try the soup I made.

13
00:02:03,480 --> 00:02:03,960
Honey,

14
00:02:04,800 --> 00:02:05,520
you've worked hard.

15
00:02:06,080 --> 00:02:07,040
You try it first.

16
00:02:29,160 --> 00:02:29,960
How is it?

17
00:02:30,320 --> 00:02:31,120
Is it good?

18
00:02:34,840 --> 00:02:36,160
It's the same taste.

19
00:02:40,440 --> 00:02:41,240
Honey,

20
00:02:42,320 --> 00:02:43,800
if Xu Meng hadn't interfered,

21
00:02:45,080 --> 00:02:45,760
we would have been

22
00:02:45,960 --> 00:02:47,120
like this a long time ago.

23
00:02:48,680 --> 00:02:49,560
Don't worry,

24
00:02:50,000 --> 00:02:51,240
I'll make up for everything

25
00:02:51,480 --> 00:02:52,960
for everything I've lost.

26
00:02:55,280 --> 00:02:56,040
As for Xu Meng,

27
00:02:58,040 --> 00:03:00,440
I will make her pay for what she did.

28
00:03:15,320 --> 00:03:16,200
With you here,

29
00:03:17,040 --> 00:03:18,160
I'm relieved.

30
00:03:32,840 --> 00:03:33,400
Honey,

31
00:03:34,520 --> 00:03:35,320
I need to get back to work.

32
00:04:14,560 --> 00:04:15,360
Vivi,

33
00:04:20,360 --> 00:04:21,160
it's me.

34
00:04:32,480 --> 00:04:33,440
Actually, that day,

35
00:04:33,600 --> 00:04:34,720
when you spoke,

36
00:04:35,200 --> 00:04:36,120
I knew

37
00:04:37,000 --> 00:04:38,520
the man with bandages was you,

38
00:04:39,040 --> 00:04:39,720
not Mengmeng.

39
00:04:49,840 --> 00:04:50,680
Xing,

40
00:04:59,040 --> 00:04:59,840
Vivi,

41
00:05:00,640 --> 00:05:02,160
Mengmeng didn't betray you.

42
00:05:02,440 --> 00:05:04,080
Everything she did was for you.

43
00:05:04,480 --> 00:05:06,320
Don't believe Lin Mojiao.

44
00:05:12,680 --> 00:05:14,760
He's the one who hurt you.

45
00:05:15,880 --> 00:05:17,160
I'll take you away.

46
00:05:18,040 --> 00:05:18,840
Xing,

47
00:05:25,200 --> 00:05:26,000
Vivi,

48
00:05:26,880 --> 00:05:27,680
let's go.

49
00:05:34,440 --> 00:05:35,400
I'm sorry.

50
00:05:39,840 --> 00:05:40,640
Honey.

51
00:05:41,920 --> 00:05:42,720
Honey.

52
00:05:43,440 --> 00:05:44,760
Help my husband.

53
00:05:46,240 --> 00:05:47,040
Help me.

54
00:05:50,040 --> 00:05:50,680
Honey.

55
00:05:51,040 --> 00:05:51,840
Don't be afraid.

56
00:06:00,640 --> 00:06:01,560
Catch the man
who just left my house.

57
00:06:07,320 --> 00:06:08,040
It's okay.

58
00:07:29,120 --> 00:07:30,000
What a loser.

59
00:07:38,200 --> 00:07:39,520
Lu Xing is so poor.

60
00:07:39,800 --> 00:07:40,120
Yeah.

61
00:07:40,640 --> 00:07:42,320
His parents divorced and abandoned him.

62
00:07:42,800 --> 00:07:44,160
How is he going to live?

63
00:08:02,240 --> 00:08:02,760
Here.

64
00:08:07,080 --> 00:08:07,720
Eat it.

65
00:08:09,640 --> 00:08:10,440
Thank you.

66
00:08:11,120 --> 00:08:11,400
Come on.

67
00:08:11,600 --> 00:08:12,560
Sit down and eat together.

68
00:08:13,080 --> 00:08:13,520
Sit.

69
00:08:14,680 --> 00:08:15,760
This is for you.

70
00:08:17,440 --> 00:08:18,240
Thank you.

71
00:08:20,720 --> 00:08:21,760
My name is Lan Hewei.

72
00:08:21,840 --> 00:08:23,160
What's your name?

73
00:08:24,680 --> 00:08:25,880
I'm Lu Xing.

74
00:08:26,040 --> 00:08:27,320
I'm Xu Meng.

75
00:08:27,320 --> 00:08:28,000
From now on,

76
00:08:28,000 --> 00:08:29,560
we're friends.

77
00:08:34,120 --> 00:08:34,760
Bye.

78
00:08:34,760 --> 00:08:35,880
Bye.

79
00:08:37,000 --> 00:08:37,640
I'm off.
I'm home.

80
00:09:11,080 --> 00:09:12,040
I'm late again.
Sorry.

81
00:09:12,560 --> 00:09:13,040
Lu Xing,

82
00:09:13,040 --> 00:09:14,160
You're late again.

83
00:09:14,480 --> 00:09:15,200
I'll take a drink as punishment.

84
00:09:15,560 --> 00:09:16,320
Forget it.

85
00:09:16,720 --> 00:09:17,520
Let's drink together.

86
00:09:18,360 --> 00:09:19,760
Here, these are for you.

87
00:09:20,040 --> 00:09:20,720
Thank you, Uncle Hu.

88
00:09:21,280 --> 00:09:21,760
It's okay.

89
00:09:22,760 --> 00:09:23,160
Come on.
Let's have a toast.

90
00:09:24,240 --> 00:09:24,800
I'll finish it.

91
00:09:26,600 --> 00:09:27,360
Drink as you please.

92
00:09:31,000 --> 00:09:31,760
Here, try this.

93
00:09:41,240 --> 00:09:42,560
What can I do?

94
00:09:43,320 --> 00:09:44,800
I can do nothing.

95
00:10:23,600 --> 00:10:25,440
You dress like an old man all day.

96
00:10:25,560 --> 00:10:27,320
It's embarrassing to be around me.

97
00:10:27,600 --> 00:10:28,400
I bought these clothes.
You can wear them for now.

98
00:10:30,040 --> 00:10:31,720
Buy new ones later.

99
00:11:26,920 --> 00:11:27,600
Here you are.

100
00:11:27,840 --> 00:11:29,200
No one will take care of you if you catch a cold.

101
00:12:25,360 --> 00:12:26,080
Where is this?
Why?

102
00:12:27,040 --> 00:12:27,600
You want to kill me?

103
00:12:28,440 --> 00:12:29,480
Why do you have to do this?

104
00:12:31,800 --> 00:12:33,120
Why do you have to do this to me?

105
00:12:33,600 --> 00:12:34,480
Let me go.
Let go.

106
00:12:36,400 --> 00:12:37,240
There's no reason.

107
00:14:38,840 --> 00:14:39,480
Where are you going?

108
00:14:48,720 --> 00:14:49,960
You look so pretty today.

109
00:14:54,240 --> 00:14:55,480
I just want to

110
00:14:55,800 --> 00:14:56,960
go out for a walk.

111
00:14:58,920 --> 00:15:00,320
Since you're so pretty,

112
00:15:01,120 --> 00:15:02,440
why not go with me to see my mother?
